title: GoPro: The Secret Life of Pets Short Film Teaser
description:
See how GoPro videos can inspire our pets to new heights in this sneak peek from GoPro: The Secret Life of Pets, the incredible short film that GoPro, Illumination and Universal are producing together. Coming to YouTube, Facebook and Instagram on July 1st. 

Live-action footage shot 100% on GoPro.

Music
Rich Aucoin, "City I Love"
